{"title":"「FJSC2018TGD1T3」 错排","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":["提高","数论"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5033#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/submissions?problem_id=5033","statistics":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5033/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5033/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/discussion/problem/5033"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"求有多少种长度为 n 的序列 A，满足以下条件：\n\n\n\n1. $1 - n$ 这 $n$ 个数在序列中各出现了一次。\n\n\n\n2. 若第 $i$ 个数 $A_i$ 的值为 $i$ ，则称 $i$ 是稳定的。序列恰好有 $m$ 个数是稳定的。\n\n\n\n满足条件的序列可能很多，序列数对 $10^9+7$ 取模。\n\n\n\n\n\n"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行一个数 $T$，表示有 $T$ 组数据。\n\n接下来 $T$ 行，每行两个整数 $n$ 、$m$。\n\n"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出 $T$ 行，每行一个数，表示求出的序列数\n\n"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"【输入样例】\n````\n5\n1 0\n1 1\n5 2\n100 50\n10000 5000\n````\n【输出样例】\n````\n0\n1\n20\n578028887\n60695423\n````\n"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$T=500000$ ，$n \\le 1000000$， $m \\le 1000000$\n\n数据有梯度。"}]}